    "This demonstrates the robustness of CircDA.",
    "Embedding enhances the predictive performance of CircDAFeature embedding and deep representation are important components of our CircDA.",
    "So, we analyze the effectiveness of feature embedding and deep representation.",
    "To investigate the effectiveness of feature embedding, we compare the performance of the CircDA with that of models without MF (named non-MF) and models without CNN (non-CNN).",
